      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPassed optional test review-dne-zfs-part-3 on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-33vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dc19e4af-207f-4216-ae6c-6ee5df029d9d ran 3 tests.",
